{"tid":349244,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【日文達人入】點睇D字幕組將歌詞譯成詩","createTime":"2017-08-06T11:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T01:33:19.000Z","uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfdb9affcbb015f1cd778a72ed8d68cd97d7669d","tid":349244,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"最近翻睇冰果, 發現有個字幕組將ed1譯成咁:<br />\n今夜與君愛夢相會<br />\n務必覓得 <br />\n微眠之約<br />\n<br />\n原文:<br />\n今夜恋にかわる しあわせな夢で会おう<br />\nきっと ねえ 見つけてね <br />\nまどろみの約束<br />\n<br />\n如果我無睇錯, 原文應該係口語<br />\n咁譯咪破壞曬個語境?"},{"pid":"177d4dbe913a26e62c62d9ef70235c800ca327d9","tid":349244,"uid":96032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得最重要係冇譯錯<br />\n樓主個case我覺得幾好，幾有feel<br />\n問題反而係譯完之後，有啲意思冇表達到<br />\n例如：<br />\nしあわせな夢で会おう --&gt; 呢句有種心急想快啲見面嘅意思，但譯成「今夜與君愛夢相會」，就冇咗咁嘅意思，變咗似係單純講事實<br />\n日文N5，首歌都未聽過，純鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fade2a7c61ff5fa219a1c02db58c2b0044c22cbe","tid":349244,"uid":29063,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc97519e9305468d2abbf9a82e5b81290a9953f4","tid":349244,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8656d9b0d82ad0deada8167c95648e78530f4412","tid":349244,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n入黎就想睇呢張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ae6f6697130c139b989859ce651092402e779d","tid":349244,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩字幕組咁型？"},{"pid":"dd599d5a8ea8c99e00f739a9f17938d55377f2ac","tid":349244,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6GBBzvz5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpn6GBBzvz5Q&d=EEyZFgnMonz3UVTUyTIdeJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=93c61c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6GBBzvz5Q</a>"},{"pid":"06df937756e9c8af0ef3d1617c9e716c16c6aa36","tid":349244,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"呢d先叫翻譯"},{"pid":"1becba0d7b6ecf5421a049e55e134f47193c5063","tid":349244,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"翻譯一向係參考，質素唔求太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d845d1fd7e41e925c3eb55f1a14006b559ba6cd3","tid":349244,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"翻譯做詩個d有時真係好難頂,不過多數都係歌個度先係咁,忍下就算"},{"pid":"2cba5ed491a90da293a656994ee42c61e6dbe591","tid":349244,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得最重要係冇譯錯<br />\n樓主個case我覺得幾好，幾有feel<br />\n問題<span style=\"color: red;\">反而係譯完之後，有啲意思冇表達到</span><br />\n例如：<br />\nしあわせな夢で会おう --&gt; 呢句有種心急想快啲見面嘅意思，但譯成「今夜與君愛夢相會」，就冇咗咁嘅意思，變咗似係單純講事實<br />\n日文N5，首歌都未聽過，純鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係講緊呢樣<br />\n歌詞本身係一個人內心讀白, 性格可能係有D文藝, 鍾意幻想<br />\n但既然遣詞用字係白話<br />\n咁翻譯應該遷就返呢樣野, 用中文嘅白話表現返個分真摯<br />\n而唔係直接用文言文"},{"pid":"4ec43f8f9f28795f02a4259186e18d8617ad25fa","tid":349244,"uid":3239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻譯做詩個d有時真係好難頂,不過多數都係歌個度先係咁,忍下就算</blockquote><br />\n最近個套來自深淵又係<br />\n<br />\n墜入深淵 無法自拔<br />\n明亮雙眸 耀勝燈火<br />\n前路漫漫 落入迷途<br />\n深入虛空 尋找真相<br />\n追尋答案 一無所有 在所不惜<br />\n空谷迴響 引人入勝 久久不息<br />\n羅盤指向 晦暗深處 斷港決潢<br />\n直面詛咒 心亦雀躍<br />\n心懷憧憬 無法抑制<br />\n<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b6697578dadc00d47b459f26107985aa58214f","tid":349244,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>翻譯做詩個d有時真係好難頂,不過多數都係歌個度先係咁,忍下就算</blockquote><br />\n最近個套來自深淵又係<br />\n<br />\n墜入深淵 無法自拔<br />\n明亮雙眸 耀勝燈火<br />\n前路漫漫 落入迷途<br />\n深入虛空 尋找真相<br />\n追尋答案 一無所有 在所不惜<br />\n空谷迴響 引人入勝 久久不息<br />\n羅盤指向 晦暗深處 斷港決潢<br />\n直面詛咒 心亦雀躍<br />\n心懷憧憬 無法抑制<br />\n<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾乎都唔留意字幕 由得佢"},{"pid":"fd1fffedbb4c32e62519ac56198812b1b32e40af","tid":349244,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n入黎就想睇呢張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938eb110db7c2c23658fc1822be82dfdec259006","tid":349244,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"信達雅是鳩旦啦"},{"pid":"fbea800d61ea12cba5f8bd3496d539661418db30","tid":349244,"uid":96032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得最重要係冇譯錯<br />\n樓主個case我覺得幾好，幾有feel<br />\n問題<span style=\"color: red;\">反而係譯完之後，有啲意思冇表達到</span><br />\n例如：<br />\nしあわせな夢で会おう --&gt; 呢句有種心急想快啲見面嘅意思，但譯成「今夜與君愛夢相會」，就冇咗咁嘅意思，變咗似係單純講事實<br />\n日文N5，首歌都未聽過，純鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係講緊呢樣<br />\n歌詞本身係一個人內心讀白, 性格可能係有D文藝, 鍾意幻想<br />\n但既然遣詞用字係白話<br />\n咁翻譯應該遷就返呢樣野, 用中文嘅白話表現返個分真摯<br />\n而唔係直接用文言文</blockquote><br />\n我覺得原文係唔係白話唔係咁重要，重要嘅係曲風<br />\n因為我唔熟日文，唔肯定原文係唔係白話<br />\n況且有時將白話原文，譯成古文風效果都唔錯<br />\n但曲風就冇得講<br />\n首歌曲風唔係古風，但將歌詞譯曬做文言文就好明顯好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講果套來自深淵就係一個好例子，明顯字幕組痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce206ae29bd3314aaba596b72ac317aeaa82a456","tid":349244,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6nsfe8r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6nsfe8r&h=04612254&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩字幕組咁型？</blockquote><br />\n冇記錯 應該係KNA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c8b3ca5b827377d3e89112e9020225ed47a302","tid":349244,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"但無可否認有d真係釋得好靚<br />\n茜さす<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4b0b0740064a20a0f601d24a39ca15896aca96","tid":349244,"uid":63888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"TVB都試過，當年真係嚇一跳<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9umkef6t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9umkef6t&h=5a131645&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a36cbf7c8c05eee660695400eac57bdcc51fb33","tid":349244,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T21:57:04.000Z","msg":"做字幕其實好辛苦<br />\n佢地係op發泄下<br />\n我又冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ccc8c512651e34a1f3aa6e67972ac144e2bec2","tid":349244,"uid":129739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做字幕其實好辛苦<br />\n佢地係op發泄下<br />\n我又冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係發泄，係show off<br />\n翻譯既原則唔應該破壞被翻譯語言既文體，假若兩者文體唔同（即中文同日文），亂咁文學化修飾，會誤導左讀者"},{"pid":"ba4b7416fce9d40f4784fb784d2dafd7fbb9ae34","tid":349244,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但無可否認有d真係釋得好靚<br />\n茜さす<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個正"},{"pid":"74356e655c94ce2091fc732ef97a1f333ef87986","tid":349244,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"啟航吧！編舟計畫首 ED又係咁<br />\n重新編詞咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca4b9fc14625bf70c2d3cec31f8d727b5864155","tid":349244,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6GBBzvz5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpn6GBBzvz5Q&d=EEyZFgnMonz3UVTUyTIdeJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=93c61c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6GBBzvz5Q</a></blockquote><br />\n睇唔ab翻譯左d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71702705fe73c5057d3104ea692c263b67bf2679","tid":349244,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pn6GBBzvz5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpn6GBBzvz5Q&d=EEyZFgnMonz3UVTUyTIdeJ7TfgnX9jywtY